+3. OHME CHARGING       → FORCE_CHARGE (EV integration)
+4. TIME SCHEDULE       → Scheduled mode (automation)
+5. DEFAULT MODE        → SELF_USE (outside ranges)
 ```
 
+**Note**: Battery protection is enforced after mode determination but before mode change execution.
